OL,3,CMan who stalked wife with crossbow
OL,4,Cbefore knife attack jailed
OL,6,FCCTV showed Stephen Carr brandishing a
OL,7,Fcrossbow and selecting a kitchen
OL,8,Fknife. Jon Hill reports
OL,10,FA man who fired at his wife with a
OL,11,Fcrossbow before repeatedly stabbing
OL,12,Fher as she called police has been
OL,13,Fjailed.
OL,15,FStephen Carr, 57, told Lorna Carr "you
OL,16,Fare dying tonight" during the attack
OL,17,Fat their home in Strensall, York.
OL,19,FHe was convicted of attempted murder
OL,20,Fafter a trial at Leeds Crown Court and
OL,21,Fjailed for 17 years.
