OL,3,CMan who stalked wife with crossbow
OL,4,Cbefore knife attack jailed
OL,6,FThe trial heard that CCTV from inside
OL,7,Fthe couple's home showed Carr
OL,8,Fbrandishing the crossbow and selecting
OL,9,Fa knife from the kitchen drawer before
OL,10,Fstalking Mrs Carr around the house on
OL,11,F8 September last year.
OL,13,FShe managed to close a door between
OL,14,Fthem, at which point he fired a bolt
OL,15,Finto the door.
OL,17,FAs she tried to escape, Mrs Carr broke
OL,18,Fa number of arrows before taking cover
OL,19,Fin a bedroom and hiding under a duvet.
