OL,3,CMan who stalked wife with crossbow
OL,4,Cbefore knife attack jailed
OL,6,FCarr fired three further shots into
OL,7,Fthe duvet.
OL,9,FAfter Mrs Carr dialled 999 the police
OL,10,Fcall handler could hear her shouting:
OL,11,F"Don't kill me Steve... Think of your
OL,12,Fmum."
OL,14,FCarr stabbed her six times in the back
OL,15,Fbefore shutting himself in the garden
OL,16,Fshed.
OL,18,FHe then sent a WhatsApp message to his
OL,19,Fwife saying: "I'm glad I didn't do
OL,20,Fwhat I wanted to do. I did say you
OL,21,Fwere pushing me."
