OL,6,FCarr was still in the shed when he was
OL,7,Farrested by officers brandishing
OL,8,FTasers.
OL,10,FMrs Carr was treated at the scene
OL,11,Fbefore being taken to Leeds General
OL,12,FInfirmary for surgery.
OL,14,FCarr pleaded guilty to causing
OL,15,Fgrievous bodily harm but denied
OL,16,Fattempted murder.
OL,18,FHe claimed he became violent due to
OL,19,Fhis wife's controlling behaviour and
OL,20,Fhad wanted to scare her into leaving
OL,21,Fhim alone.
