OL,3,CMan who stalked wife with crossbow
OL,4,Cbefore knife attack jailed
OL,6,FHe said the pressure of working full
OL,7,Ftime, caring for his elderly mother
OL,8,Fand alcohol addiction contributed to
OL,9,Fhis mental state.
OL,11,FA North Yorkshire Police spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "He said he never intended to
OL,13,Fkill his wife and that if he wanted to
OL,14,Fkill her with the bow, his skills as
OL,15,Fan archer would allow him to do so."
OL,17,FHe claimed he could not recall
OL,18,Fstabbing Mrs Carr, suggesting he had
OL,19,F"blacked out".
