OL,4,Cbefore knife attack jailed
OL,6,FDuring the sentencing hearing, the
OL,7,Fcourt heard Mrs Carr believed her
OL,8,Fhusband's actions were a "one off" and
OL,9,Fshe would visit him in prison and
OL,10,Fplanned to resume their relationship
OL,11,Fafter his release.
OL,13,FAfter the sentencing, Det Ch Insp
OL,14,FJonathan Sygrove said: "It's hard to
OL,15,Fimagine the terror the victim felt
OL,16,Fbeing shot at with a bow and arrows,
OL,17,Fthen set on with a knife by her own
OL,18,Fhusband.
