OL,6,F"This was also a harrowing incident
OL,7,Ffor our officers and control room
OL,8,Fstaff who responded to the 999 call,
OL,9,Fand their professionalism ensured Carr
OL,10,Fwas promptly located and arrested
OL,11,Fbefore anything further could happen.
OL,13,F"While we apply high levels of
OL,14,Fdiscretion when we deal with domestic
OL,15,Fviolence, it's also important we raise
OL,16,Fawareness and highlight the work we do
OL,17,Fto tackle it, so people have the
OL,18,Fconfidence to come forward."
